# FACT SHEET

## Australian Energy Efficiency Framework - Andrew Baker

### Current Situation
- Fuel Excise Revenue (2023-24): $15.71 billion
- EV Adoption Rate: 12.4%
- Australian Fuel Import Dependency: ~90%

### Proposed Framework Impact
- Revenue Replacement: $17.9B (114%)
- Economic Multiplier: 4.35x
- Jobs Created: 100,000 by 2030
- Energy Reduction: 35-45%

